$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux Pro board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Zybo Z7 out-of-box demo — vector buses.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Live peripherals: HDMI raster, audio sine, ADC, etc.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 4 ! leds $end
$var wire 4 " sws $end
$var wire 4 # btn $end
$var wire 1 $ led_rgb_5 $end
$var wire 1 % led_rgb_6 $end
$var wire 16 & hdmi_in_data $end
$var wire 1 ' hdmi_in_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 ( hdmi_in_hsync $end
$var wire 1 ) hdmi_in_vsync $end
$var wire 1 * hdmi_in_de $end
$var wire 16 + hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 1 , hdmi_out_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 - hdmi_out_hsync $end
$var wire 1 . hdmi_out_vsync $end
$var wire 1 / hdmi_out_de $end
$var wire 16 0 audio_codec_mic_in $end
$var wire 16 1 audio_codec_headphone_out $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
